"abhihariyati."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn17:69.29"
msgid "Ettha, deva, chandaṃ pajaha jīvite apekkhaṃ mākāsī’ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><h2>
msgctxt "dn17:70.1"
msgid "8. Brahmalokūpagama"
msgstr "Rebirth in the Brahmā Realm"

#. </h2><p><a class="sc" id="53"></a><a class="wp" id="wp2.13"></a><a
#. class="pts" id="pts2.196"></a>
msgctxt "dn17:71.1"
msgid "Atha kho, ānanda, rājā mahāsudassano na cirasseva kālamakāsi."
msgstr "Not long after that, King Mahāsudassana passed away."

msgctxt "dn17:71.2"
msgid ""
"Seyyathāpi, ānanda, gahapatissa vā gahapatiputtassa vā manuññaṃ bhojanaṃ "
"bhuttāvissa bhattasammado hoti;"
msgstr ""
"And the feeling he had close to death was like a householder or their child "
"falling asleep after eating a delectable meal."

#, fuzzy
msgctxt "dn17:71.3"
msgid "evameva kho, ānanda, rañño mahāsudassanassa māraṇantikā vedanā ahosi."
msgstr " "

msgctxt "dn17:71.4"
msgid "Kālaṅkato ca, ānanda, rājā mahāsudassano sugatiṃ brahmalokaṃ upapajji."
msgstr ""
"When he passed away King mahāsudassana was reborn in a good place, a Brahmā "
"realm."

#. VAR: kumārakīḷaṃ → ... kīḷitaṃ (bj, mr) | ... kīḷikaṃ (pts1)
msgctxt "dn17:71.5"
msgid "Rājā, ānanda, mahāsudassano caturāsīti vassasahassāni kumārakīḷaṃ kīḷi."
msgstr "Ānanda, King Mahāsudassana played children’s games for 84,000 years."

msgctxt "dn17:71.6"
msgid "Caturāsīti vassasahassāni oparajjaṃ kāresi."
msgstr "He ruled as viceroy for 84,000 years."

msgctxt "dn17:71.7"
msgid "Caturāsīti vassasahassāni rajjaṃ kāresi."
msgstr "He ruled as king for 84,000 years."

#. VAR: brahmacariyaṃ cari → brahmacariyaṃ ācari (s1-3, km) |
#. brahma­cari­ya­macari (mr)
#. VAR: gihibhūto → gihībhūto (bj, pts1) | gīhibhūto (km)
msgctxt "dn17:71.8"
msgid "Caturāsīti vassasahassāni gihibhūto dhamme pāsāde brahmacariyaṃ cari."
msgstr ""
"He led the spiritual life as a layman in the Palace of Principle for 84,000 "
"years."

msgctxt "dn17:71.9"
msgid ""
"So cattāro brahmavihāre bhāvetvā kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā brahmalokūpago "
"ahosi."
msgstr ""
"And having developed the four Brahmā meditations, when his body broke up, "
"after death, he was reborn in a good place, a Brahmā realm."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="54"></a><a class="wp" id="wp2.14"></a><a
#. class="pts" id="pts2.197"></a>
msgctxt "dn17:72.1"
msgid "Siyā kho panānanda, evamassa:"
msgstr "Now, Ānanda, you might think:"

msgctxt "dn17:72.2"
msgid ""
"‘añño nūna tena samayena rājā mahāsudassano ahosī’ti, na kho panetaṃ, "
"ānanda, evaṃ daṭṭhabbaṃ."
msgstr "‘Surely King Mahāsudassana must have been someone else at that time?’"

#, fuzzy
msgctxt "dn17:72.3"
msgid "Ahaṃ tena samayena rājā mahāsudassano ahosiṃ."
msgstr ""
"But you should not see it like that. I myself was King Mahāsudassana at that "
"time."

msgctxt "dn17:72.4"
msgid ""
"Mama tāni caturāsīti nagarasahassāni kusāvatīrājadhānippamukhāni, mama tāni "
"caturāsīti pāsādasahassāni dhammapāsādappamukhāni, mama tāni caturāsīti "
"kūṭāgārasahassāni mahāviyūhakūṭāgārappamukhāni, mama tāni caturāsīti "
"pallaṅkasahassāni sovaṇṇamayāni rūpiyamayāni dantamayāni sāramayāni "
"gonakatthatāni paṭikatthatāni paṭalikatthatāni "
"kadalimigapavarapaccattharaṇāni sauttaracchadāni ubhatolohitakūpadhānāni, "
"mama tāni caturāsīti nāgasahassāni sovaṇṇālaṅkārāni sovaṇṇadhajāni "
"hemajālapaṭicchannāni uposathanāgarājappamukhāni, mama tāni caturāsīti "
"assasahassāni sovaṇṇālaṅkārāni sovaṇṇadhajāni hemajālapaṭicchannāni "
"valāhakaassarājappamukhāni, mama tāni caturāsīti rathasahassāni "
"sīhacammaparivārāni byagghacammaparivārāni dīpicammaparivārāni "
"paṇḍukambalaparivārāni sovaṇṇālaṅkārāni sovaṇṇadhajāni hemajālapaṭicchannāni "
"vejayantarathappamukhāni, mama tāni caturāsīti maṇisahassāni "
"maṇiratanappamukhāni, mama tāni caturāsīti itthisahassāni "
"subhaddādevippamukhāni, mama tāni caturāsīti gahapatisahassāni "
"gahapatiratanappamukhāni, mama tāni caturāsīti khattiyasahassāni anuyantāni "
"pariṇāyakaratanappamukhāni, mama tāni caturāsīti dhenusahassāni "
"duhasandanāni kaṃsūpadhāraṇāni, mama tāni caturāsīti vatthakoṭisahassāni "
"khomasukhumānaṃ kappāsikasukhumānaṃ koseyyasukhumānaṃ kambalasukhumānaṃ, "
"mama tāni caturāsīti thālipākasahassāni sāyaṃ pātaṃ bhattābhihāro "
"abhihariyittha."
msgstr ""
"Mine were the 84,000 cities, with the royal capital of Kusāvatī foremost. "
"And mine were all the other possessions."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="55"></a><a class="wp" id="wp2.15"></a><a
#. class="pts" id="pts2.198"></a>
msgctxt "dn17:73.1"
msgid ""
"Tesaṃ kho panānanda, caturāsītinagarasahassānaṃ ekaññeva taṃ nagaraṃ hoti, "
"yaṃ tena samayena ajjhāvasāmi yadidaṃ kusāvatī rājadhānī."
msgstr "Of those 84,000 cities, I only stayed in one, the capital Kusāvatī."

msgctxt "dn17:73.2"
msgid ""
"Tesaṃ kho panānanda, caturāsīti pāsādasahassānaṃ ekoyeva so pāsādo hoti, yaṃ "
"tena samayena ajjhāvasāmi yadidaṃ dhammo pāsādo."
msgstr "Of those 84,000 mansions, I only dwelt in one, the Palace of Principle."

msgctxt "dn17:73.3"
msgid ""
"Tesaṃ kho panānanda, caturāsīti kūṭāgārasahassānaṃ ekaññeva taṃ kūṭāgāraṃ "
"hoti, yaṃ tena samayena ajjhāvasāmi yadidaṃ mahāviyūhaṃ kūṭāgāraṃ."
msgstr "Of those 84,000 chambers, I only dwelt in the great foyer."

msgctxt "dn17:73.4"
msgid ""
"Tesaṃ kho panānanda, caturāsīti pallaṅkasahassānaṃ ekoyeva so pallaṅko hoti, "
"yaṃ tena samayena paribhuñjāmi yadidaṃ sovaṇṇamayo vā rūpiyamayo vā "
"dantamayo vā sāramayo vā."
msgstr ""
"Of those 84,000 couches, I only used one, made of gold or silver or ivory or "
"heartwood."

msgctxt "dn17:73.5"
msgid ""
"Tesaṃ kho panānanda, caturāsīti nāgasahassānaṃ ekoyeva so nāgo hoti, yaṃ "
"tena samayena abhiruhāmi yadidaṃ uposatho nāgarājā."
msgstr ""
"Of those 84,000 bull elephants, I only rode one, the royal bull elephant "
"named Sabbath."

msgctxt "dn17:73.6"
msgid ""
"Tesaṃ kho panānanda, caturāsīti assasahassānaṃ ekoyeva so asso hoti, yaṃ "
"tena samayena abhiruhāmi yadidaṃ valāhako assarājā."
msgstr ""
"Of those 84,000 horses, I only rode one, the royal horse named Thundercloud."

msgctxt "dn17:73.7"
msgid ""
"Tesaṃ kho panānanda, caturāsīti rathasahassānaṃ ekoyeva so ratho hoti, yaṃ "
"tena samayena abhiruhāmi yadidaṃ vejayantaratho."
msgstr "Of those 84,000 chariots, I only rode one, the chariot named Triumph."

# https://discourse.suttacentral.net/t/is-there-such-a-word-as-velamika/2952
#. VAR: vessinī → velāmikānī (si, pts1) | vessāyinī (s1-3, km) | velāmikā
#. (^sn22.96#1 [96. Gomaya­piṇḍa­sutta])
msgctxt "dn17:73.8"
msgid ""
"Tesaṃ kho panānanda, caturāsīti itthisahassānaṃ ekāyeva sā itthī hoti, yā "
"tena samayena paccupaṭṭhāti khattiyānī vā vessinī vā."
msgstr ""
"Of those 84,000 women, I was only served by one, a maiden of the "
"aristocratic or merchant classes."

msgctxt "dn17:73.9"
msgid ""
"Tesaṃ kho panānanda, caturāsīti vatthakoṭisahassānaṃ ekaṃyeva taṃ dussayugaṃ "
"hoti, yaṃ tena samayena paridahāmi khomasukhumaṃ vā kappāsikasukhumaṃ vā "
"koseyyasukhumaṃ vā kambalasukhumaṃ vā."
msgstr ""
"Of those 8,400,000,000 cloths, I only wore one pair, made of fine linen, "
"cotton, silk, or wool."

msgctxt "dn17:73.10"
msgid ""
"Tesaṃ kho panānanda, caturāsīti thālipākasahassānaṃ ekoyeva so thālipāko "
"hoti, yato nāḷikodanaparamaṃ bhuñjāmi tadupiyañca sūpeyyaṃ."
msgstr ""
"Of those 84,000 servings of food, I only had one, eating at most a serve of "
"rice and suitable sauce."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="56"></a><a class="wp" id="wp2.16"></a>
msgctxt "dn17:74.1"
msgid "Passānanda, sabbete saṅkhārā atītā niruddhā vipariṇatā."
msgstr ""
"See, Ānanda! All those conditioned phenomena have passed, ceased, and "
"perished."

msgctxt "dn17:74.2"
msgid "Evaṃ aniccā kho, ānanda, saṅkhārā;"
msgstr "So impermanent are conditions,"

msgctxt "dn17:74.3"
msgid "evaṃ addhuvā kho, ānanda, saṅkhārā;"
msgstr "so unstable are conditions,"

msgctxt "dn17:74.4"
msgid "evaṃ anassāsikā kho, ānanda, saṅkhārā."
msgstr "so unreliable are conditions. "

msgctxt "dn17:74.5"
msgid ""
"Yāvañcidaṃ, ānanda, alameva sabbasaṅkhāresu nibbindituṃ, alaṃ virajjituṃ, "
"alaṃ vimuccituṃ."
msgstr ""
"This is quite enough for you to become disillusioned, dispassionate, and "
"freed from all conditions."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="57"></a><a class="wp" id="wp2.17"></a><a
#. class="pts" id="pts2.199"></a>
msgctxt "dn17:75.1"
msgid ""
"Chakkhattuṃ kho panāhaṃ, ānanda, abhijānāmi imasmiṃ padese sarīraṃ "
"nikkhipitaṃ, tañca kho rājāva samāno cakkavattī dhammiko dhammarājā "
"cāturanto vijitāvī janapadatthāvariyappatto sattaratanasamannāgato, ayaṃ "
"sattamo sarīranikkhepo."
msgstr ""
"Six times, Ānanda, I recall having laid down my body at this place. And the "
"seventh time was as a wheel-turning monarch, a just and principled king, at "
"which time my dominion extended to all four sides, I achieved stability in "
"the country, and I possessed the seven treasures."

msgctxt "dn17:75.2"
msgid ""
"Na kho panāhaṃ, ānanda, taṃ padesaṃ samanupassāmi sadevake loke samārake "
"sabrahmake sassamaṇabrāhmaṇiyā pajāya sadevamanussāya yattha tathāgato "
"aṭṭhamaṃ sarīraṃ nikkhipeyyā”ti."
msgstr ""
"But Ānanda, I do not see any place in this world with its gods, Māras, and "
"Brahmās, this population with its ascetics and brahmins, its gods and humans "
"where the Realized One would lay down his body for the eighth time.”"

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="58"></a>
msgctxt "dn17:76.1"
msgid "Idamavoca bhagavā."
msgstr "This is what the Buddha said."

msgctxt "dn17:76.2"
msgid "Idaṃ vatvāna sugato athāparaṃ etadavoca satthā:"
msgstr "Then the Holy One, the Teacher, went on to say: "

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p><a class="sc" id="59"></a>
msgctxt "dn17:77.1"
msgid "“Aniccā vata saṅkhārā,"
msgstr "“Oh! Conditions are impermanent,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn17:77.2"
msgid "uppādavayadhammino;"
msgstr "their nature’s to rise and fall;"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn17:77.3"
msgid "Uppajjitvā nirujjhanti,"
msgstr "having arisen, they cease; "

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn17:77.4"
msgid "tesaṃ vūpasamo sukho”ti."
msgstr "their stilling is true bliss.”"

#. </p></blockquote><p class="endsutta">
msgctxt "dn17:78.1"
msgid "Mahāsudassanasuttaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ catutthaṃ."
msgstr ""
